data.description: This gorgeous 4 bedroom 2.5  bathroom home is located in the highly desirable Spring Grove Plantation. Upon entering, you'll be greeted by hardwood floors, tons of natural light, brand new carpet downstairs and an ample amount of space. The kitchen features beautiful cabinets, stainless steel appliances, a pantry, breakfast nook area and views of every room downstairs. The unique layout of the open living room/ kitchen area has a great amount of space for everyone and includes a separate room off the living area that can be used as a playroom, office, game room...etc. Large separate dining room offers space for everyone. Upstairs you'll find a huge primary bedroom featuring a large walk-in closet en-suite with separate tub/ shower and double vanities. The other spacious bedrooms share a beautiful guest bathroom. The upstairs laundry room features a lot of space and storage. Step outside to your relaxation paradise where you'll find plenty of room to sit back on your screened in porch and enjoy the enormous fully fenced in backyard.
